      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MI AMIGO DIABLO (3) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and two placings. Was out of the placings last time (24.05) at Bendigo in a Group Listed, finishing seventh and beaten 5 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. CACO MISSILE (4) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (30.10) behind Paw Varna at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. LISA ROSE (2) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her convincing win a few runs back, getting around Sale over 510m in 28.71. Has the ability and looks a key chance. CASH IN VIEW (8) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
